         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">3/2/88. ¶  ¶ The Eucalypt with the reddish filaments that you sent, ¶  esteemed Mr Tepper, is the large-flowered form of  ¶ E. gracilis ¶ . The species is better described in the  ¶ Fragmenta  ¶ and i...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">88.02.03a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Tepper</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M198, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">3/2/88.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Die Eucalypte, mit den röthliche Filamenten, welche Sie senden, geehrter Herr Tepper, ist die grossblüthige Form von E. gracilis. Die Art ist besser in den Fragm. u in der Eucalyptogr. beschrieben als in der Flora Austr. Wenn Jemand, den Sie kennen, nahe dem Platz wohnt, könnte er wohl Samen davon sammeln, da es eine nette Var. für Cultur in Park-Anlagen wäre.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Der <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name> ist eigentlich </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">zu dürftig</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> für critische Untersuchung; es mag eine der allgemeinen europäischen Arten sein, dort dann immigrirt.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihre Abhandlung ist per Post registrirt mit einem Beifolge-Brief von mir an den Secr. der Tasm R.S. bereits abgegangen.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Freundlichst grüssend</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">3/2/88.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Eucalypt with the reddish filaments that you sent,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See Tepper's annotation on M to O. Tepper, 28 January 1888.</p>
               </note> esteemed Mr Tepper, is the large-flowered form of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">E. gracilis</seg>. The species is better described in the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Fragmenta </seg>and in the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Eucalyptographia</seg> than in the <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Flora australiensis</seg>.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B60.05.01, p. 55; B79.13.11, Decade 3; Bentham (1863-78), vol. 3, p. 211.</p>
               </note>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>If anyone you know lives near the place, he could probably collect seeds of it, as it would be a nice variety for culture in parks.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name>
               </seg> is really <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">too meagre</hi>
               </seg> for critical investigation; it may be one of the common European species, then introduced there.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your paper has already gone off by registered post with an enclosed letter from me to the Secretary of the Royal Society of Tasmania.<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Letter not found. Tepper's paper on <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Xanthorrhoea</seg> was not published by the Royal Society of Tasmania; see M to O. Tepper, 28 January 1888.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Friendliest greetings</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Eucalyptus%20gracilis">Eucalyptus gracilis</name>
            </p>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Scleranthus">Scleranthus</name>
            </p>
         </div>
